，关闭虚拟机，windows-server-2012.img文件即是模板文件。\r\n\r\nh1. 4、相关教程连接：\r\n\r\n《OpenStack镜像制作》：[[http://blog.chinaunix.net/uid-22414998-id-3272059.html]]',NULL,NULL,3,NULL,2,NULL,2,1,'2014-06-09 09:59:05','2014-06-09 09:59:27','2014-06-09',100,NULL,NULL,262,1,2,0,NULL),(263,3,50,'[Wiki 注册] Wiki在注册的时候，无法发送确认邮件','h2. 1、问题：\r\n\r\n在一些用户注册完之后，发现收不到确认邮件\r\n\r\nh2. 2、问题解决：\r\n\r\n没有将dns配置写到网卡配置文件中，导致重启网卡后，wiki主机无法解析邮箱地址域名',NULL,NULL,3,NULL,2,NULL,2,0,'2014-06-09 10:08:17','2014-06-09 10:08:17','2014-06-09',0,NULL,NULL,263,1,2,0,NULL),(264,2,50,'[Wiki 账号] Wiki账号及服务器信息','h1. （1）登录域名：\r\n\r\nh2. [[http://wiki.foxitsoftware.com]]\r\n\r\nh1. （2）管理员账号/密码：\r\n\r\nh2. 用户名：admin\r\n密码：foxit2013!@#$%\r\n\r\nh1. （3）服务器信息：\r\n\r\nh2. IP地址：118.192.9.200    \r\n用户名/密码：root/kevinstar\r\n配置文件路径：/etc/mediawiki/LocalSettings.php\r\nmysql数据存储目录：/home/data',NULL,NULL,3,NULL,2,NULL,2,1,'2014-06-09 10:26:51','2014-06-09 10:27:07','2014-06-09',100,NULL,NULL,264,1,2,0,NULL),(265,3,2,'Mb02 Transport service is down','清除队列','2014-06-06',NULL,3,4,2,NULL,4,0,'2014-06-09 10:42:03','2014-06-09 10:42:03','2014-06-06',0,NULL,NULL,265,1,2,0,NULL),(266,2,51,'G区5号楼','*1、H3C S7600* \r\n   password:admin\r\n*2、cisco 3900* \r\n   password：foxit@0311\r\n*3、Foxit-WIFI* \r\n   password:foxit87801276\r\n*4、Foxit-WIFI-5G* \r\n   password:foxit87801276\r\n*5、H3C WX3024 无线控制器*\r\n   ID:admin password：foxit0103\r\n*6、linux路由器*\r\n   ID：root password：kevinstar\r\n*7、宽带*\r\n*联通*\r\nIP:58.22.60.34（思科路由）35（linux路由）,36、37（vpn）\r\n掩码：255.255.255.248\r\n网关：58.22.60.33  \r\nDNS: 58.22.96.66\r\n*移动*\r\nIP: 112.5.141.172(保利通) ;112.5.141.173;（cisco路由器）112.5.141.174（linux路由）;112.5.141.176;112.5.141.177.\r\n掩码：255.255.255.0\r\n网关：112.5.141.1\r\nDNS: 211.138.151.161\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,2,NULL,10,1,'2014-06-09 17:11:43','2014-06-10 13:26:52','2014-06-10',0,NULL,NULL,266,1,6,0,NULL),(267,2,51,'水木清华帐号密码','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,2,NULL,3,0,'2014-06-10 13:26:52','2014-06-10 13:26:52','2014-06-10',0,NULL,266,266,2,3,0,NULL),(268,2,51,'ID OF ABOU